Package: REPLesentR
Title: Presentations in the REPL
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sebastian", "Warnholz", email = "wahani@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: You can do your presentation in the console but write your slides in RMarkdown or any other text format. For this we provide a modular system to generate slide decks for the display in the R REPL. This project is inspired by the REPLesent project for presentations in the Scala REPL.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.2)
Imports: modules, dat, tools, knitr
Suggests: testthat,
    covr
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
